### Get All Institutions
GET http://localhost:8080/rede-segura/api/institutions
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Institution by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/rede-segura/api/institutions/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a New Institution
POST http://localhost:8080/rede-segura/api/institutions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Instituto Federal de Educação",
  "address": {
    "street": "Rua das Flores, 123",
    "city": "Natal",
    "state": "RN",
    "country": "Brasil",
    "postalCode": "59000-000"
  },
  "type": "Universidade",
  "contact": "contato@if.edu.br"
}


###

### Update an Existing Institution
PUT http://localhost:8080/rede-segura/api/institutions/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Instituto Federal de Educação E Tecnologia",
  "address": {
    "street": "Rua da Ametista, 123",
    "city": "Sao Paulo",
    "state": "RN",
    "country": "Brasil",
    "postalCode": "59000-000"
  },
  "type": "Universidade",
  "contact": "contato@if.edu.br"
}


###

### Delete an Institution
DELETE http://localhost:8080/rede-segura/api/institutions/4
Accept: application/json
